data.description: New Price! Act Now! Investor or Owner-Occupied Opportunity! Perfect for Buy & Hold Rental or your own residence. Move-in ready, 2019-built, 4BR/2BA home with open floor plan, vinyl plank flooring, gas kitchen, Espresso cabinets, and fenced-in yard. Main bedroom downstairs with exterior access & en-suite bath. Spacious additional bedrooms & full bath upstairs. Private, ready-to-customize backyard. Neutral tones throughout. Centrally located between Fort Sam/BAMC & Randolph AFB. Ideal for creating a rental income stream or customizing your own dream home. Don't miss this chance!
